OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry morning with long
OL,6,Fsunny spells but showers developing
OL,7,Ftowards midday. Further showers and
OL,8,Fsunny spells through the afternoon,
OL,9,Fthe showers moving through quickly on
OL,10,Fthe strengthening northerly breeze.
OL,11,FRather cold.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLate sunny spells, then,
OL,14,Fespecially for Orkney, clear spells
OL,15,Fovernight with showers. Cloudier for
OL,16,FShetland, perhaps more persistent
OL,17,Frain, through the early hours. Strong
OL,18,Fnortherly breeze, risk of gales
OL,19,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
