OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny rain across Shetland soon
OL,6,Fclearing then a bright, but cold, day
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells and a few showers.
OL,8,FStrong northerly or northwesterly
OL,9,Fwinds slowly easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry with sunny spells Saturday with
OL,13,Fnorthwesterly winds easing. Morning
OL,14,Frain Sunday but becoming brighter for
OL,15,Fthe afternoon with a few showers.
OL,16,FRather cloudy Monday with rain at
OL,17,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
